{"data":{"page":{"id":"146b7ede-7538-5810-8224-1c58fe5e7bdf","html":"<p class=\"work-links\">\n<a class=\"btn icon icon-external\" href=\"http://newtir.es\" target=\"_blank\">Launch website</a>\n</p>\n<p>\n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 1000px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 63.3%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/f1a3603dc890242e8545629956a16280/877ff/1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f1a3603dc890242e8545629956a16280/d2504/1.jpg 500w,\n/static/f1a3603dc890242e8545629956a16280/877ff/1.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  </p>\n<p>Newtir asked me to build a Joomla website to showcase their company’s services and corporate info. The website features standard static pages with login area and contact form.</p>","fields":{"prefix":"16 September 2009"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Newtir","cover":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/newtir/","source":"work"}}